26\\times$,\n$1.43\\times$, $1.40\\times$ on average on NVIDIA's RTX 2070 GPU, V100 GPU, and\nIntel's Xeon 8259CL CPU, respectively. Collage has been open-sourced and\ndeployed in Apache TVM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 02:01:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 03:03:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2022 02:20:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-31"}
