 on\nmodel design for the community in the future. Code is available at:\nhttps://github.com/fxmeng/RMNet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 04:07:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-02"}
