15 edition by \"thescrivener\" is in the public domain. This edition is\nan extended and revised version by Mateo Carmona with the collaboration of\nUlrik Buchholtz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Nov 2021 15:01:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Nov 2021 15:52:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-23"}
